    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. UQ has been performed via Monte Carlo propagation of the three primary input parameters, yielding a 95th-percentile NIH within the RH < 1 acceptance band. The assessment team acknowledges that sensitivity analysis to identify dominant input drivers has not been completed; this is planned as a future extension. On balance, the existing evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision at the declared assurance level.",
